A video has surfaced on the internet, where a lady alleged that the upcoming singer, Portable Omolalami carried her for one night’s enjoyment, and what they both did in the night turned to pregnancy.
Recalled that about 2 weeks ago, Singer, Portable became popular after he met the popular Nigerian musician, Olamide. His slang and song, titled, Zazoo Zehh became the trending song as he featured popular singer, Olamide and Nigerian dancer, Poco Lee.
The lady, who identified herself as Abike said, “Portable had fun with me last year, and it turned to pregnancy. He gave me money to abort the pregnancy but I didn’t do it because it abomination to abort a pregnancy in my family. I heard that Portable is now a celebrity. He has not been sending money to me and my child. He’s not picking my calls again. Please help me share the video”
